Package de.sukit.chatbot

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ChatBotApplication
    Spring Boot class.
    DictionaryHandler
    DictionaryHandler reads the data/dictionary.json-file into a String,String HashMap.
    DictionaryModel
    Represents an entry in the dictionary list.
    FileWatcher
    The FileWatcher class creates a FileWatcher which solely monitors the data-directory in which our dictionary.json-file resides in.
    Main
    Main class used for setting up default files and ensuring our dictionary is loaded and monitored by a filewatcher.
